        "name": "Counterattack",
        "description": "Focus on defensive manoeuvres. Gives you +${preHitEffect0modValue0}% Melee Maximum Hit for each attack blocked for the duration of this attack (Stacks up to ${preHitEffect0maxStacks} times). Follow up with an unavoidable counterattack that deals ${attackDamageMaxValue0}% of your normal damage.",
